(52, 1, '2014-07-26 21:05:39', '2014-07-26 21:05:39', '[BMo_scrollGallery id=1 sG_thumbPosition=bottom sG_images=1 duration=slow gallery_width=920 gallery_height=690 thumbs_width=20 thumbs_height=20 sG_caption=1 sG_start=1 sG_loop=1 sG_loopThumbs=0 sG_clickable=1 sG_opacity=100 sG_area=0 sG_scrollSpeed=1 sG_autoScroll=0 sG_aS_stopOnOver=1 sG_diashowDelay=0 sG_followImages=1 sG_responsive=1 ]\r\n\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://www.heytes.com/property2/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--615" alt="" />\r\nTucked away in a most peaceful cul de sac and overlooking a large green area No. 71 boasts all the characteristics of a rural setting, yet is within close proximity of Blessington Village and all services. Extended to accommodate 3 bedrooms this bright and spacious semi detached bungalow is presented in excellent condition with a very desirable aspect to compliment a small attractive garden.\r\n\r\n<strong>Features</strong>\r\n\r\nBeautifully proportioned Victorian residence with many original period features intact\r\n\r\nOn-street resident parking permits\r\nBeautiful rear garden with rear access\r\nImpressive tree-lined road within 3 kilometres of city centre, adjacent to the Luas and striking distance to Heuston Station, Phoenix Park and the M50\r\nGFCH\r\nAlarmed\r\nc. 137.32 sq m/1478 sq ft\r\nBER: E2\r\nBER No.: 106644974\r\nEnergy Performance Indicator: 355.87 kWh/m/yr\r\n\r\n<strong>Ground Floor</strong>\r\n\r\nHallway: 7.22m x 1.62m (238 x 54)\r\nOriginal wood floor. Dado rail. Original cornicing. Alarm. Stain glass side lights and fan light at front door. Downstairs w.c. with wash hand basin and tiled floor. Phone point.\r\n\r\nReception 1: 4.09m x 3.79m (135 x 125)\r\nOriginal wood floor. Original cornicing. Original marble fireplace with gas fire, tiled hearth and surround. TV point. Original double doors to...\r\n\r\nReception 2: 3.86m x 3.82m (128 x 126)\r\nOriginal wood floor. Original cornicing. Original marble fireplace with tiled surround and slate hearth. TV point.\r\nKitchen: 7.53m x 3.07m (248 x 101)\r\nTiled floor. Cast iron Godin solid fuel stove. Fully fitted floor and wall units in high gloss white. Stainless steel sink unit. Gas boiler. Dual fuel cooker. Extractor fan. Tiled splashback. Zanussi dishwasher. Whirlpool washing machine. Central fireplace.\r\n\r\n<strong>1st Floor Return</strong>\r\nLanding: 4.26m x 0.78m (14 x 27)\r\nLarge shelved hot press with immersion. Dado rail.\r\n\r\nBathroom: 3.3m x 2.15m (1010 x 71)\r\nTiled floor. Wood panelling below dado rail. Heated towel rail. Attic access. Wall heater. Cast iron roll top bath with brass globe taps. W.c. with over head cistern. Wash hand basin with brass fittings. Separate shower cubicle. Fully tiled with Mains shower.\r\n\r\nBedroom 3: 3.01m x 2.88m (911 x 95)\r\nPhone point. Original cast iron\r\n\r\n<strong>1st Floor</strong>\r\n\r\nLanding: 5.15m x 1.88m (1611 x 62)\r\nVelux window. Dado rail. Original cornicing. Stairs to attic.\r\n\r\nBedroom 1: 3.9m x 3.84m (1210 x 127)\r\nOriginal cornicing. Original cast iron fireplace with tiled hearth. Built in wardrobes with internal lighting.\r\nBedroom 2: 3.84m x 3.8m (127 x 126)\r\nOriginal cornicing. Original cast iron fireplace with tiled hearth. Built in wardrobes with internal lighting. Bay window.\r\n\r\nBedroom 4: 2.65m x 2.12m (88 x 611)\r\nBox room. Original cornicing.\r\n\r\n<strong> Outside</strong>\r\nGarden: 15.15m x 5.83m + 9.18m x 2.5m (498 x 192) + (301 x 82)\r\nPart lawn. Part deck with mature planting and trees. Lean to shed. Decked area included double doors to rear lane. Covered area with lighting. Storage shed. Covered area by back door for bikes and bins.\r\n\r\n<strong>Viewing</strong>\r\nBy prior appointment only.', 'No. 71 Westpark, Blessington, Co. Wicklow', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'no-71-westpark-blessington-co-wicklow', '', '', '2014-08-18 16:39:33', '2014-08-18 16:39:33', '', 0, 'http://www.heytes.com/property2/?post_type=prope