(424, 1, '2014-08-13 23:22:43', '2014-08-13 23:22:43', '<div class="section group">\r\n<div class="col span_1_of_2">\r\n<h2>Renting a Property?</h2>\r\nAre you thinking of renting a property now or in the coming months? We have rented many properties in Wicklow, Kildare, Carlow and Dublin region over the past 20 years so we have an excellent knowledge of rental market prices in these areas. Fill in your details below we will be in touch to arrange a free rental review of your property. Alternatively call us directly on 045-865555.\r\n[si-contact-form form=''3'']\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col span_2_of_2">\r\n<h2>Why Choose Nugent Auctioneers?</h2>\r\nWhatever property you wish to let, we can assist whether it be a family home, apartment, semi-detached house, farm or commercial premises. We pride ourselves on the quality of our staff and their ability to deliver high levels of personal service. The difference is that we really care when organising the letting of a large commercial farm or a small cottage.\r\n\r\nOur goal is to give the best advice based on our knowledge and research. We can provide a personal service ranging from simply finding a tenant to a full management service and we can help you through the minefield of tenancy legislation. In finding a tenant, we strive to provide a professional service employing traditional values and modern methods of marketing.\r\n\r\n<h3>Letting Services</h3>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\r\n	<li>An Extensive database of potential tenants</li>\r\n	<li>Local office presence</li>\r\n	<li>Regional and local advertising</li>\r\n	<li>Worldwide website presence with all properties listed nugents.ie and daft.ie</li>\r\n	<li>Informative letting particulars</li>\r\n	<li>Accompanied viewings</li>\r\n	<li>Careful tenant selection and credit checks</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of tenancy agreements and inventories</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Property Management Service</h3>\r\n<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">\r\n	<li>Collect t