(428, 1, '2014-08-13 23:26:51', '2014-08-13 23:26:51', '<div class="section group">\r\n<div class="col span_1_of_2">\r\n<h2>Free Valuation Service</h2>\r\nAre you thinking of selling now or in the coming months? We have sold many properties in Wicklow, Kildare, Carlow and Dublin region over the past 20 years so we have an excellent knowledge of property values in these areas. Fill in your details below we will be in touch to arrange a free valuation of your property. Alternatively call us directly on 045-865555.\r\n[si-contact-form form=''1'']\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col span_2_of_2">\r\n<h2>Residential Sales</h2>\r\nNugent Auctioneersis a long established firm covering the areas of West Wicklow, Kidare, Carlow, East Wicklow and South Dublin. A reputation for honesty, commitment and progressive, innovative marketing has been gained over 20 years of involvement in the ever changing property world.\r\n\r\nOver the years we have adopted the latest technology to promote our clients'' home to the best advantage and also offer a seamless route for buyers to locate the property of their dreams.Our local and regional coverage is extensive, distinctive and supported by uploads to national leading web portals including MyHome.ie and Daft.ie. Wecarefully match hard copy, email brochure distribution and SMS text alerts to buyers.\r\n\r\nNugents ''For Sale'' boards remain one of the most eye catching and familiar sights in this region.\r\n\r\nAs a firm we have an extensive portfolio of properties, be it first time buyer apartments or cottages, through to traditional and contemporary family homes, and more imposing country houses. Irrespective of price, every client benefits from the dedication and enthusiasm of our extensively trained staff, the comprehensive knowledge of our managers and negotiators, but above all our determination to offer the best service available.\r\n\r\nFrom the moment we provide our carefully considered pricing advice, through to the point of exchange of contracts and completion, our clients can be assured of the highest quality of ''one to one'' service, built on years of experience at the forefront of the Wickow, Kildare, Carlow and Dublin property markets.\r\n\r\nIf you have a property to sell contact directly on 045-86555 for a free valuation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Residential Sales', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '324-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-13 23:26:51', '2014-08-13 23:26:51', '', 324, 'http://www.heytes.com/property2/uncategorized/324-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
