(437, 1, '2014-08-14 10:31:27', '2014-08-14 10:31:27', '<h2>Estate agents in Blessington</h2>\r\nNugent Auctioneers is a leading independent estate agent established for over 20 years covering areas of West Wicklow, Kildare, Carlow, East Wicklow, Dublin South and Dublin West. We tailor our services to each client and situation and we have all necessary expertise to secure and manage the sale or rental of your property. We always aim to keep the process of selling or purchasing property for sale as simple as possible. We know how daunting and complicated it can be.\r\n\r\nNugent Auctioneers has been operating as an estate agent in Blessington for over 20 years and has earned a reputation as one of the most innovative and well known independent estate agents in the region. We are ideally positioned to offer a range of services that extend well beyond simple sales and lettings, such as planning advice, property management, refurbishment advice and regular up-to-date feedback on the progress of your property listings. Our website enables you to receive relevant property alerts. You will also be able to review the marketing work that we do on your behalf.\r\n<h2>Customer-centred approach</h2>\r\nWe believe in supplying our clients with current information to ensure that they are able to make the best decisions possible. Our quarterly newsletter has informative articles on aspects of the current property market. Our guidelines for residential sales and lettings, which ensure that when you consult with Nugent Auctioneers you have the background information necessary to make the most of the sales or rental process.\r\n\r\nNugent Auctioneers also work with other estate agents around Ireland to provide an holistic overview of properties and prices nationwide. With all of our experience in the industry, we have learnt what it takes to meet client expectations and pride ourselves on being one of the most client-focused estate and letting agents in the region and the immediate s