(527, 1, '2014-08-17 01:06:54', '2014-08-17 01:06:54', 'This impressive 6 bed detached home is in a wonderful location, on an elevated 2.02 hectare (c. 5 acre) site with commanding views of the spectacular surrounding countryside. The property is light filled with spacious rooms extending to c. 372 sq mtrs (c. 4000 sq ft). This ideal family home has recently undergone major refurbishment and is located in a quiet rural setting away from the main road which is extremely private. The garden and shrubberies are well maintained and there are a selection of outbuildings and stables, also in excellent condition. The house is set back approximately 700m from the road and is reached by a private concrete driveway. Ballinacrow Stud has a high level of thermal insulation throughout and double glazing with thermaglaze. A new heating oil boiler and tank were fitted in 2006 and a new fitted kitchen in the same year.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://www.heytes.com/property2/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--528" alt="" />\n\n&nbsp;', 'Ballinacrow Stud, Stratford on Slaney, Co. Wicklow', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '464-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-08-17 01:06:54', '2014-08-17 01:06:54', '', 464, 'http://www.heytes.com/property2/uncategorized/464-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
