(529, 1, '2014-08-17 02:11:47', '2014-08-17 02:11:47', 'No. 50 is a 4 bed end of terrace family home finished to the highest of standards overlooking a green area and in a quiet cul de sac location. In showhouse condition this property benefits from its large patio area and garden to rear perfect for entertaining in the Summer months. The property is walking distance of Blessington with all its services &amp; amenities and within easy commuting distance of Dublin City Centre.\r\n\r\n[BMo_scrollGallery id=8 sG_thumbPosition=bottom sG_images=1 duration=slow gallery_width=920 gallery_height=690 thumbs_width=20 thumbs_height=20 sG_caption=1 sG_start=1 sG_loop=1 sG_loopThumbs=0 sG_clickable=1 sG_opacity=100 sG_area=0 sG_scrollSpeed=1 sG_autoScroll=0 sG_aS_stopOnOver=1 sG_diashowDelay=0 sG_followImages=1 sG_responsive=1 ]\r\n<img class="ngg_displayed_gallery mceItem" src="http://www.heytes.com/property2/nextgen-attach_to_post/preview/id--591" alt="" />', 'No. 50 Blessington Orchard, Blessington, Co. Wicklow', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'no-50-blessington-orchard-blessington-co-wicklow', '', '', '2014-08-17 02:18:20', '2014-08-17 02:18:20', '', 0, 'http://www.heytes.com/property2/?post_type=property&#038;p=529', 0, 'property', '', 0),
